    "created_at": "2017-03-22T11:32:12Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-03-22T14:10:42Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I would second @GraionDilach point here as players are not in the world in layman terms. (Even if they technically are you get my point right?)\r\n\r\nEdit: This can be fixed by filtering the player actors out of the array in line 170 of OpenRA.Mods.Common/Scripting/Global/MapGlobal.cs\r\n```\r\n[Desc(\"Returns a table of all the actors that are currently on the map/in the world.\")]\r\npublic Actor[] ActorsInWorld { get { return world.Actors.Where(\r\n    a => (Check actorinfo if this is a player actor or if a == a.Owner.Actor)).ToArray(); } }\r\n```"
  },
